<p>Not only is the Palace one of the city’s most interesting buildings from a historic point of view, it’s also home to the most beautiful artworks in all of Venice. You may not be an art critic specialized in Italian Renaissance art, but the paintings that you will find here boast the signature of the greatest Venetian masters of all time, including Titian, Tintoretto and Veronese. <br>Enchanting, fascinating, and gorgeous from several points of view, Venice will surprise you, no matter how much you have travelled around before ending up here.<br></p>